    <body><div type="edition" n="urn:cts:latinLit:tmp1081.tmp1081.opp-lat1">
					<head>
						<title type="main">- FERRANDI DIACONI EPISTOLA AD EGYPPIUM.. DB ESSENTIA TRINITATIS AC
							DUABUS CHRISTI NATURIS</title>
					</head>
					<p>
						<milestone unit="PLSection" n="u"/>
					</p>
					<ab>
						<title type="sub">Domino beatissimo fratri Egyppio. presbytero Ferran­ dus exiguus in
							Domino salutem.</title>
					</ab>
					<p>Carissiine, considera quales habeat vires ab Ariano <lb/> comite nuper proposita
						quæstio, sed prius quibus <lb/> inter se sententiis vel dogmatibus Ariani et catholici
							<milestone unit="PLSection" n="u"/><lb/> differant, deliberemus. Ariani volunt
						individuam <lb/> Trinitatem prædicare, sicut Scriptuiræ prædicant <lb/> unum Deum ;
						catholici vero præcepta legis salubri­ <lb/> ter audientes, etc.<note type="footnote"> '
							Retiqua vicle,is inter Ferrandi Diu(on; opera qure mox sumus edituri. EDIT </note></p>
					<pb n="855"/>

				</div>
